def_cn: 不可抵抗的;不可抗拒的;不能压制的
def_en: If you describe something such as a desire or force as irresistible, you mean that it is so powerful that it makes you act in a certain way, and there is nothing you can do to prevent this.

def_cn: 吸引人的;富有诱惑力的
def_en: If you describe something or someone as irresistible, you mean that they are so good or attractive that you cannot stop yourself from liking them or wanting them.
